headline: FactSet Declares Dividend
summary: NORWALK, Conn., Feb. 05, 2026 (GLOBE NEWSWIRE) -- FactSet (NYSE:FDS | NASDAQ:FDS), a global financial digital platform and enterprise solutions provider, today announced that its Board of Directors approved a regular quarterly cash dividend of $1.10 per share. The cash dividend will be paid on March 19, 2026, to holders of record of FactSet’s common stock at the close of business on February 27, 2026.
